<br>
&quot;I don't think just a feeling could make someone crazy.  Perhaps there was a reason for you being here.  Or maybe it just was curiosity that brought you.  Which ever, I'm glad you came.  It's always nice to see a new face around here.&quot;<br>
<br>
She wanted to say more, but held her tongue.  She had a special interest for this Amazon, that had oddly developed quickly.  In her past she was known for loving men, but that was before she was brought back from the Spirit Realm.  Perhaps she was a new woman, now. <p>_.·.Øtere, §hamaness of the N¤rth.·._<br>
